frames.caption: A majestic anthropomorphic wolf stands confidently on a rocky surface, surrounded by swirling clouds and an imposing wave. The wolf wears ornate blue armor with fur accents, and its eyes glow with an intense blue light. The scene conveys a sense of power and mysticism, set against a dramatic natural backdrop.
